deploy schema:

1.copy cgi script to a common cgi path, e,g:
cp get-flv.py /usr/lib/cgi-bin/
(grep cgi -rIn /etc/apache2/
ScriptAlias /cgi-bin/ /usr/lib/cgi-bin/)

2.copy php file to web server dir
mkdir /var/www/hhac
cp *.php /var/www/hhac
cp *.swf /var/www/hhac

3.create database user & database
mysql -u root -p -e setup_db.sql

4.add users & videos

